R Notebook

Annotate the full 9MBO dataset 1. Use Random Forest Model (RFM) - train model from Annotated hMO subset 2. Correlation assignment model (CAM) - run correlation 3. Use Seurat label transfer - transfer labels from annotated hMO subset

For each prediction method visualize on UMAP and get frequency of cell type predictions per cluster (bar chart and df)

# add experiment date
Idents(seu) <- "Batch"

names(cluster.ids) <- levels(seu)
seu <- RenameIdents(seu, cluster.ids)
